snippet.title: Boyfriend Dungeon: Date Your Weapons Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
It’s up to you to plunder the “dunj” and take your weapons on dates. Capture the hearts of cuties to level them up. Boyfriend Dungeon is the the playful shack-and-slash the world’s been waiting for! Coming 2019.

Wishlist on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/674930/Boyfriend_Dungeon/

Website: http://www.boyfrienddungeon.com
Hear our full (original!) song: https://soundcloud.com/marskye/without-a-weapon-featuring-madeleine-mcqueen
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/kitfoxgames
